+++ Howto Build +++

Always build the plugin with Groovy 1.7. Otherwise BytecodeInterface8 from Groovy 1.8 is not found when running the plugin.

* use CodeNarc-Update-Site (Release or Snapshot) project
* open site.xml with "Site Manifest" editor
* select "org.codenarc.eclipse"
* press "Build All" button

+++ Howto Test +++

* install release jars
* project
  * run check
  * clear markers
* files
  * run single file check
  * run multi-selection check
  * clear markers
* Eclipse and Groovy
  * Eclipse 3.5
    * Groovy 1.7
  * Eclipse 3.6
    * Groovy 1.7
    * Groovy 1.8
  * Eclipse 3.7
    * Groovy 1.7
    * Groovy 1.8
  * Eclipse 4.2
